 Wiggles 凭借锐舞混音版官方专辑跻身澳大利亚顶级舞曲音乐排行榜https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wiggles-top-dance-music-chart-in-australia-with-official-album-of-rave-remixes-3752405?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=澳大利亚 the-wiggles 顶级舞曲音乐排行榜以及锐舞混音版官方专辑Anagricel DuranWed, 01 May 2024 13:59:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsDancePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3752405 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 3 月 25 日，澳大利亚悉尼，The Wiggles、Wiggly Friends 和 Captain Feathersword 在环形码头的皇家加勒比游轮“海洋赞礼号”前。 （由 Rocket Weijers/Getty Images 为皇家加勒比 ANZ 拍摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张专辑在排行榜上超越了 Sia 和 Rufus du Sol 等人</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wiggles-top-dance-music-chart-in-australia-with-official-album-of-rave-remixes-3752405">The Wiggles 凭借锐舞混音版官方专辑跻身澳大利亚顶级舞曲音乐排行榜，并</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 3 月 25 日，澳大利亚悉尼，The Wiggles、Wiggly Friends 和 Captain Feathersword 在环形码头的皇家加勒比游轮“海洋赞礼号”前。 （由 Rocket Weijers/Getty Images 为皇家加勒比 ANZ 拍摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wiggles">The Wiggles</a>凭借其官方锐舞混音专辑登上了澳大利亚舞曲排行榜的榜首。</p><p>他们最新的 LP“The Wiggles Soundsystem: Rave of Innocence”收录了该乐队一些经典热门歌曲的 14 首 EDM 混音版，例如“Hot Potato”、“Fruit Salad”、“Toot Toot、Chugga Chugga、Big Red Car”和该乐队的新热门歌曲“Bouncing Balls”的改编版。</p><p>该专辑一经发行就在 ARIA 澳大利亚舞曲专辑排行榜上名列第一。它由获得多白金奖和 ARIA 提名的艺术家、DJ 兼制作人 Lenny Pearce（也是现任紫色 Wiggle John 的双胞胎兄弟）和 DJ Dorothy the Dinosaur 重新混音。 Pearce 拥有超过 130 万<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tiktok">TikTok</a>粉丝，喜欢他定期对不太可能的儿童音乐曲调和其他新颖歌曲进行流行 EDM 混音。</p><p> 《The Wiggles Soundsystem: Rave of Innocence》在排行榜上的排名超过了<a href="/artists/Sia">Sia</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rufus-du-sol">Rufus du Sol</a>等大牌艺术家的作品。获得第一名凸显了这个著名儿童乐队对新听众和对原创歌曲怀有怀旧热爱的长期粉丝的广泛吸引力。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：Wiggles 音响系统：Rave of Innocence" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/1ZZnrkjq3sKWHwEkvtHLdp?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3752420" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752420" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752420" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="“The Wiggles Soundsystem_ Rave of Innocence”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/The-Wiggles-Soundsystem_-Rave-of-Innocence-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752420" class="wp-caption-text"> “The Wiggles Soundsystem_ Rave of Innocence”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>“The Wiggles Soundsystem：Rave of Innocence”曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>“猴子之舞（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“摇滚再见你的熊（Wiggles 音响系统混音版）”</strong><br /> <strong>“烫手山芋（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“划，划，划你的船（Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“章鱼亨利（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“BINGO（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;ABC（The Wiggles 音响系统混音版）&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“Toot Toot、Chugga Chugga、Big Red Car（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“水果沙拉（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“弹跳球（The Wiggles 音响系统混音版）”</strong><br /> <strong>“五只小鸭子（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“摇摆狗，他喜欢探戈（Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“小鲨鱼（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong><br /> <strong>“一闪一闪亮晶晶（The Wiggles 音响系统混音）”</strong></p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这张 LP 时，The Wiggles 的 Anthony Field 表示：“看到 20 多岁和 30 多岁的人们以一种全新的有趣方式欣赏我们的音乐，这真是令人难以置信，这张混音专辑在某种程度上是这一点的延伸。 。这是一次疯狂的旅程。”</p><p>专辑发行后，The Wiggles 和 DJ Dorothy 计划于 2024 年在澳大利亚各地的成人夜总会举办一系列 DJ 演出。</p><p>新的锐舞现场表演于三月份在墨尔本的 Hello Sunshine 音乐节上首次亮相，场场爆满，观众们见证了乐队向舞曲音乐强国的转变。</p><p>其他新闻方面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/australia-spotify-wrapped-2023-most-streamed-artists-3551109">The Wiggles、The Kid LAROI 和 Flume 是去年 Spotify 上播放量最高的澳大利亚本地艺术家</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-wiggles-top-dance-music-chart-in-australia-with-official-album-of-rave-remixes-3752405">The Wiggles 凭借锐舞混音版官方专辑跻身澳大利亚顶级舞曲音乐排行榜，并</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
