s-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3365052" class="wp-caption-text"> Dragon Quest的宝藏。信用：Square Enix。</figcaption></figure><p> “游戏市场中客户的口味已经多样化，客户来享受各种流派的内容。市场越来越多地两极分化，但我觉得我们已经开发了许多属于中间的头衔。我想提出更清晰的区别，”他补充说。</p><p>该新闻报道说， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-7-rebirth"><em>《最终幻想7：重生》</em></a>的表现不佳，仅出售了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-7-remake">《最终幻想7：翻拍》</a></em>的一半。 “我不希望这对这一点上的第三款游戏的范围会产生重大影响，但是它可能会导致Square Enix重新考虑其处理方式如何处理依赖先前基地的直接续集的方法标题，”分析师丹尼尔·艾哈迈德（Daniel Ahmad）告诉<a href="https://www.inverse.com/gaming/square-enix-abandoned-games-ff7-rebirth-sales#:~:text=Final%20Fantasy%207%20Rebirth%20reportedly%20fell%20below%20sales%20targets%20for%20Square%20Enix.&amp;text=Without%20mid%2Dbudget%20titles%20to,be%20more%20important%20than%20ever." target="_blank" rel="noopener">倒数</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《最终幻想 VII 重生》最终预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q56cRDseTGQ?start=3&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在过去的一周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/outriders-studio-people-can-fly-cancels-co-op-action-rpg-project-dagger-3751114">中，由于游戏中的“缺乏资金”，</a>而<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto">Grand Theft Auto</a></em> Publisher <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/take-two">Take-Two</a>也确认，它已经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/grand-theft-auto-publisher-take-two-lays-off-hundreds-of-staff-and-cancels-games-3618889">裁定了数百名员工并取消了A，因此</a><a href="https://www